title: The Lone Ranger S01E06&E08
description:
The Lone Ranger

The Sole Survivor of a posse of Texas Rangers ambushed by a gang of desperados, John Reid was left for dead and nursed back to health by Tonto (Jay Silverheels), a friendly Indian whom he had once helped. With a black mask and silver bullets from the mine he discovered with his brother, one of the slain Rangers, Reid sets out astride his horse, Silver, to right the wrongs of the West as The Lone Ranger (Clayton Moore)

Episode 08 The Renegades

Attacks on the supply trains to the Washita Reservation, blamed on "The Renegades", are really the work of the agent in charge, Jim Lackey (Harry Havey), and a band of Army deserters led by Bolan (Gene Roth). Then,

Episode 06 War Horse

The owner of a Wild West show offers Matt Madrigo (Leonard Penn) $10,000 for Black Cloud, the famous "War Horse" of Lame Bear (CHief Yolatchie), but Madrigo's not too particular about how he gets him.

Approximately 48 Minutes 
Converted from VHS
